    "en": {
      "name": "Battlewasp - Sachi the Ritual Bow",
      "effect": "1 Insect Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters\nIf this card is Synchro Summoned: You can treat it as a Tuner. Once per turn: You can return 1 Continuous Spell you control to the hand; you can Normal Summon 1 \"Battlewasp\" monster during your Main Phase this turn, in addition to your Normal Summon/Set. (You can only gain this effect once per turn.) If this card is sent to the GY as Synchro Material: You can inflict 100 damage to your opponent for each of your banished \"Battlewasp\" monsters. You can only use this effect of \"Battlewasp - Sachi the Ritual Bow\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
